The paper proposes a new communication scheme for UAVs that involves optimizing the trajectory and power allocation to maximize energy efficiency. This falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper deals with the issue of secrecy communication, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The optimization problem involves joint design of trajectory and power allocation, which is a problem in control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.AI).
